	 <td valign=top><span class=sm>[<a class=sm href="#quests">Quests</a> | <a class=sm href="#end">Comments</a> ]</span><hr size=1>This item is the result of a quest.<br> <li><a href=quest.html?quest=2641>Adventurer's Stone</a></li><br><hr size=1><a name="quests"></a><b>Quests:</b> This item is used in quests. <img class=iho src="/shared/hide_content.gif" onClick="return toggle(this,'quest');"><div id=quest></ul><b>Butcherblock Mountains</b><ul style="margin: 1,0,3,30;"><li><a href="quest.html?quest=2659">Adventure in the Mistmoore Catacombs</a></li>
