</ul><b>Everfrost Peaks</b><ul style="margin: 1,0,3,30;"><li><a href="quest.html?quest=2662">Adventure in Miragul's Menagerie</a></li>
</ul><b>Northern Desert of Ro</b><ul style="margin: 1,0,3,30;"><li><a href="quest.html?quest=2661">Adventure in Takish-Hiz</a></li>
