</ul></div><hr size=1><br>Found in:<li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Faydwer/Butcher.htm">Butcherblock Mountains</a></li><br><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/EComm.htm">East Commonlands</a></li><br><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Everfrost.htm">Everfrost Peaks</a></li><br><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/NRo.htm">Northern Desert of Ro</a></li><br><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/SRo.htm">Southern Desert of Ro</a></li><br><hr size=1>This is needed to use the LDoN ports. Increases in power as you get more information from the <a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/faction.html?faction=364">Wayfarers Brotherhood</a>.  Maxed stats shown.</td>
