	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=190926><span id=Sage>KyrosKrane</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>55 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.07]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>The game remembers which bit of information you got last.&nbsp;&nbsp;You don't lose out if you forget to hail the person; you can &quot;save up&quot; your messages and get them all in one shot if you wish.<br><br>If you complete, say, four successful adventures (which would earn you two new messages) before you talk to the person, you will get a message after you hail him the first time saying something like, &quot;You have more information to discover.  Hail this person again.&quot;  Just hail him over and over until you get the &quot;you must adventure more&quot; message.  You'll get all the messages and credit towards your stone for all the adventures you've won.</p>&nbsp;<br>--<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=554854 target=akztarg>KyrosKrane Sylvanblade</a><br>Crusader of Erollisi Marr<br>Raid Officer, <a href=HTTP://www.sanctus-aemilius.com target=akztarg>Sanctus Aemilius</a><br>Grandmaster Blacksmith (250 + Grandmaster Smith's Hammer)<br>Grandmaster Baker (250 + Grandmaster Baker's Spoon)<br>Master Brewer, Fletcher, Jeweler, Potter, and Tailor</td></td></tr>
