	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=68019><span id= >Girazze</span></a><br><span id=notbold>2 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.66]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>For every 10 you complete in any zone, you will get a change in stats of the stone. In your case, if you complete one more success in Everfrost, you get a stat increase. Then if you complete 6 more successes in Mistmoore, you get ANOTHER stat increase. You get a stat increase for EVERY 10 successes out of any zone. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
